  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Through training and persistence inspired by the Great Purge of Stavian I, you have learned to detect the sources of divine magic in such effects' auras.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Ability to cast detect magic as a spell or spell-like ability.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you use detect magic to determine the strength and location of the aura of a functioning spell, if that spell's caster used a holy symbol as a divine focus to cast the spell, you see a ghostly image of the deity's holy symbol as part of the spell's aura. Effects that block divination spells or effects also block the effects of this feat.",
